<lyrics>[V1]
 A hlatpi tlangcungah vailamtahnak a dir, Temh ningzah hmelchunhnak a
 si, Sihmanhseh misual ca ka Bawipa a thihnak, Vailamtah nak cu ka
 tlaihchan.

[C1]
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaihchan ko, Ka nunnak kha a dongh hlan tiangin,
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaih lai i, Sui luchin sung ah ka thlen te lai.

[V2]
 Vailamtahnak zeitluk vawlei zomhtaih a in, Siseh kei ca duhnak a si,
 Pathian Tuufa a vancung sunpar kaltak in, Kalvary ah thihnak a in.

[C2]
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaihchan ko, Ka nunnak kha a dongh hlan tiangin,
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaih lai i, Sui luchin sung ah ka thlen te lai.

[V3]
 Vailamtahnak a thiang thi aa nehmi cungah, Ka hmuh aa dawhnak
 khuaruahhar, Vailam cungah Jesuh temhinnak in a thi, Keimah sualnak
 thianter awk ah.

[C3]
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaihchan ko, Ka nunnak kha a dongh hlan tiangin,
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaih lai i, Sui luchin sung ah ka thlen te lai.

[V4]
 Vailamtahnak zungzal dinnak in ka zulh lai, Lunglawm in ningzah ka in
 lai, Vancung ka inn ah khin a ka auh te lai i, A sunparnak kha kaa hrawm
 ve lai.

[C4]
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaihchan ko, Ka nunnak kha a dongh hlan tiangin,
   Vailamtahnak cu ka tlaih lai i, Sui luchin sung ah ka thlen te lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<title>VAILAM TAHNAK CH138</title>
</song>